=Employees and internal staff #Argenti's Principle 3 (Slide 9)\: "Communicate with Employees First - Internal communication must precede external statements." Slide 16 reinforced\: "Priority Rule\: Communicate with internal stakeholders FIRST, before external announcements (Argenti, 2002)."
~Investors and shareholders #Investors are external stakeholders - after employees.
}

