::Post-Crisis Communication::According to lecture, when should post-crisis stakeholder communication (closing the loop) occur?{
~Immediately when the crisis is resolved (same day) #Immediately (same day) is too soon - you haven't had time for proper analysis and learning.
=Within 1-2 weeks of resolution #Slide 22 specified\: "Timeline\: Post-crisis communication should occur within 1-2 weeks of resolution (while still relevant) but after immediate urgency passes."
